attributes.title: Honda C70 EV conversion
attributes.description:
Created on February 25, 2010 by EvehicleTechnology on Sourcemap.org:

1981 Honda C70 EV conversion. Gasoline motor removed. Electric motor added.
Lead acid batteries to be used. They can be recycled.
